EThe%20reduction%20in%20match%20fees%20has%20caused%20concern%20among%20players%20and%20the%20board%20is%20also%20considering%20spending%20less%20on%20development%20of%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20head%20of%20domestic%20cricket%20in%20the%C2%A0PCB%2C%20Abdullah%20Khurrum%20Niazi%2C%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Breducing%20facilities%26quot%3B%20for%20domestic%20players%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20players%20who%20were%20first%20being%20offered%20accommodation%20at%20five-star%20and%20four-star%20hotels%20are%20now%20being%20offered%20cheaper%20accommodation.%20Air%20travel%20has%20also%20been%20reduced%20for%20them%20besides%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20said%20that%20outstanding%20payments%20from%20last%20season%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20cleared%20for%20players%20and%20umpires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%C2%A0PCB%C2%A0is%20yet%20to%20implement%20an%20annual%20pension%20increase%20for%20former%20Test%20cricketers%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20board%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%2C%20according%20to%20one%20source%2C%20is%20that%20while%20match%20fees%20for%20players%20are%20being%20reduced%2C%20officials%20taking%20these%20decisions%20are%20getting%20monthly%20salaries%20in%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0PCB%C2%A0at%20the%20same%20time%20is%20also%20paying%20hefty%20monthly%20salaries%20to%20national%20selectors%20and%20even%20mentors%20appointed%20with%20five%20teams%20for%20the%20just-concluded%20Champions%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741916580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fr716d8s_d_625x300_13_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmore-humiliation-for-pakistan-cricketers-all-50-go-unsold-in-the-hundred-draft-7915626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%2050%20Pakistan%20players%20-%2