ghting%20police%20failures%20and%20the%20state's%20inaction.%20It%20has%20reported%20on%20the%20demolition%20of%20an%20abandoned%20mosque%20in%20Chilkur%2C%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20dupatta%20from%20minority%20schoolgirls'%20uniforms%2C%20and%20the%20government's%20failure%20to%20protect%20Waqf%20properties.%20Munsif%20has%20also%20raised%20delayed%20salaries%20of%20imams%20and%20muezzins%2C%20non-payment%20of%20stipends%20for%20divorced%20women%2C%20and%20the%20Congress's%20failure%20to%20include%20a%20Muslim%20representative%20in%20the%20Telangana%20cabinet-just%20as%20it%20had%20criticized%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20by%20Ather%20Moin%2C%20the%20newspaper's%20Executive%20Editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Revanth%20government%20expects%20us%20to%20convince%20our%20readers%20that%20Telangana%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20land%20of%20milk%20and%20honey%20under%20Congress%20rule%2C%20then%20that%20is%20something%20we%20cannot%20do.%20Instead%2C%20we%20shall%20continue%20to%20ask%3A%20Why%20have%20lands%20turned%20barren%3F%20Why%20has%20starvation%20forced%20the%20poor%20to%20the%20brink%3F%20Why%20have%20helpless%20daughters%20been%20violated%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20has%20also%20targetted%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20pointing%20to%20his%20statement%20in%20Washington%20in%20June%202023%2C%20where%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFreedom%20of%20the%20press%20is%20under%20threat%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20world%20can%20see%20it.%20A%20free%20press%20is%20vital%20to%20a%20functioning%20democracy%2C%20and%20everyone%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20accept%20criticism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BNearly%20every%20Urdu%20newspaper%20in%20the%20country%20has%20criticized%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20yet%20not%20a%20single%20one%20has%20had%20its%20central%20government%20ads%20revoked.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Revanth's%20Congress%20government%20has%20chosen%20to%20punish%20Munsif%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201975%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20tried%20to%20silence%20the%20press-and%20failed.%20Today%2C%20her%20party%20is%20repeating%20history.%20But%20let%20it%20be%20known%3A%20The%20pen%20is%20still%20mightier%20than%20the%20sword.%20Journalism%20in%20India%20will%20not%20be%20silenced%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741888980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ft55bugjg_urdu-daily-munsif_625x300_13_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-telanganas-urdu-daily-published-blank-editorial-7918730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Urdu%20daily%20in%20Telangana%20has%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20in%20protest%20against%20what%20it%20claims%20is%20the%20freezing%20of%20government%20advertisement%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Revanth%20Reddy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intel's%20new%20CEO%20Lip-Bu%20Tan%20has%20a%20history%20as%20a%20successful%20underdog%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741888932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fintel-s-new-ceo-lip-bu-tan-has-a-history-as-a-successful-underdog-125031301300_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tan%2C%20named%20Intel%20CEO%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20faces%20an%20enormous%20challenge%20in%20turning%20around%20the%20operations%20of%20a%20company%20that%20put%20the%20%26quot%3Bsilicon%26quot%3B%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fintel-s-new-ceo-lip-bu-tan-has-a-history-as-a-successful-underdog-125031301300_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%