%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20there%20are%20provisions%20that%20indicate%20that%20the%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20should%20not%20be%20carried%20out%20until%20the%20national%20census%20is%20conducted%20after%202026.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20central%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20this%20process%20to%20the%20fore%20before%20the%20census%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Ministers%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Punjab%20have%20already%20been%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20Joint%20Action%20Committee%20(JAC)%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%20been%20spearheading%20the%20opposition%20to%20delimitation%20--%20the%20exercise%20to%20redraw%20constituencies%20on%20basis%20of%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20state%20contends%20that%20against%20the%20untrammelled%20population%20of%20northern%20states%20that%20would%20increase%20their%20seats%20in%20parliament%2C%20its%20success%20with%20family%20planning%20would%20only%20penalise%20it%20with%20a%20reduced%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20and%20his%20son%20and%20Deputy%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20have%20asked%20newlyweds%20to%20have%20children%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20win%20200-plus%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%202026%20elections.%20I%20request%20the%20couples%20who%20are%20getting%20married%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20childbirth%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Our%20state%20implemented%20birth%20control%20first%2C%20and%20due%20to%20this%2C%20we%20are%20now%20facing%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20yesterday%20after%20presiding%20over%20a%20mass%20wedding%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%2C%20the%20state%20with%2039%20seats%20might%20lose%20up%20to%20eight%20seats%20in%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20while%20northern