are%20system.%20Indian%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20recent%20unscheduled%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20negotiate%20a%20trade%20deal%20and%20mitigate%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20tariffs%20on%20India's%20pharmaceutical%20exports.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20US%20relies%20heavily%20on%20Indian%20generic%20medicines%2C%20with%20nearly%20half%20of%20all%20generic%20drugs%20consumed%20in%20the%20US%20originating%20from%20India.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20significant%20savings%20for%20the%20US%20healthcare%20system%2C%20with%20estimates%20suggesting%20that%20Indian%20generics%20saved%20the%20US%20%24219%20billion%20in%202022%20alone%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20by%20consulting%20firm%20IQVIA.%20Generic%20drugs%2C%20which%20are%20cheaper%20versions%20of%20brand-name%20medications%2C%20account%20for%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20prescriptions%20in%20the%20US%2C%20making%20India's%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20a%20critical%20component%20of%20the%20US%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20proposed%20tariffs%20could%20disrupt%20this%20delicate%20balance.%20Experts%20warn%20that%20the%20tariffs%20could%20make%20some%20Indian%20generics%20unviable%2C%20leading%20to%20drug%20shortages%20and%20exacerbating%20existing%20healthcare%20issues.%20Dr.%20Melissa%20Barber%2C%20a%20drug%20costing%20expert%20from%20Yale%20University%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20tariffs%20could%20%26quot%3Bworsen%20the%20demand-supply%20imbalances%26quot%3B%20and%20disproportionately%20affect%20the%20uninsured%20and%20poor%2C%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckg8ke45gq0o%5C%22%3EBBC.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20these%20tariffs.%20Companies%20like%20Sun%20Pharma%20and%20Cipla%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20viability%20of%20their%20businesses%20in%20the%20face%20of%20increased%20tariffs.%20Dilip%20Shanghvi%2C%20chairman%20of%20Sun%20Pharma%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20justify%20relocating%20our%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20the%20significant%20cost%20differences%20between%20manufacturing%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20already%20seen%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20with%20the%20cost%20of%20raw%20materials%20for%20drugs%20increasing%20by%2020%25%20since%20Trump%20took%20office.%20The%20pharmaceutical%20sector%20is%20India's%20largest%20industrial%20export%2C%20with%20the%20US%20being%20a%20critical%20market%20for%20Indian%20generics.%20Any%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20by%20the%20US%20would%20increase%20costs%20for%20both%20generic%20medicines%20and%20specialty%20drugs%2C%20affecting%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20millions%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20mitigate%20these%20risks%2C%20some%20experts%20suggest%20that%20India%20should%20drop%20its%20tariffs%20on%20pharma%20goods%2C%20which%20would%20have%20a%20negligible%20impact%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy.%20Ajay%20Bagga%2C%20a%20veteran%20market%20expert%2C%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20%26quot%3BUS%20drug%20exports%20into%20India%20are%20barely%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%20so%20the%20impact%20will%20be%20negligible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Pharmaceutical%20Alliance%20(IPA)%20has%20also%20recommended%20zero%20duty%20on%20US%20drug%20exports%20to%20avoid%20reciprocal%20levies.%20However%2C%20this%20may%20not%20be%20a%20straightforward%20solution%2C%20as%20it%20would%20require%20significant%20changes%20to%20India's%20trade%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20situation%20unfolds%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20potential%20trade%20deal%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India.%20Mark%20Linscott%2C%20former%20assistant%20US%20trade%20representative%2C%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3Bin